                            <comment id="14243906" author="blerer" created="Fri, 12 Dec 2014 09:26:14 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Just 1 nit: &lt;br/&gt;
It would be nice to also add a unit test in &lt;tt&gt;SingleColumnRelationTest&lt;/tt&gt; for 2.1. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
